---
title: Quick Korean Ginger Chicken & Corn Slaw Bowl with Fried Egg & Spring Onion
description: This sizzling hot Korean-style chicken from the pan is an unparalleled delight. Delicious marinated beef and the joy of simplicity are winners in this dish. Topped off with a fried egg, this meal is a brilliant twist on a weeknight dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

